'''Mâ-lòi Pan-tó''' (馬來半島, [[Yîn-ngî]]: Malay Peninsula) vi-yî [[Â-chû]] thai-liu̍k chui nàm-tôn, he [[Tûng-nàm-â]] chûng-nàm pan-tó ke yit-ke chú-yeu Pan-tó, lâu [[Sû-mùn-tap-lia̍p-tó]] kak-tén [[Mâ-liuk-kap Hói-hia̍p‎]], he [[Thai-phìn-yòng]] lâu [[Yin-thu-yòng]] ke fûn-kie sien. 
Mâ-lòi Pan-tó sông yû [[Mâ-lòi-sî-â]], [[Thai-koet]], [[Mién-thien]] sâm-ke koet-kâ.
